content: Banchhanidhi Dash - KIIT School of Computer Engineering Skip to content Go to KIIT Home pageKIIT HomeProf. Achyuta Samanta Founder – KIIT & KISS achyutasamanta.com Banchhanidhi Dash Banchhanidhi Dash Banchhanidhi Dash Assistant ProfessorDr. Banchhanidhi Dash has completed his Ph.D. in CSE from KIIT, Deemed to be University, Bhubaneswar. He has more than 10 years of teaching and research experience in the field of high performance computer architecture. Currently, he is working as an Assistant professor (II) in the school of Computer Engineering in KIIT, Deemed to be University, Bhubaneswar. He has also worked as an Assistant professor in the department of computer science & Engineering (CSE) in JIGJIGA University, Addis Ababa, Ethiopia. He has published a many research papers in various International journals and conferences.
